# OpenBible data is cloned by netlify.toml at build time, not committed
Bible-Geocoding-Data/

# Generated data files — regenerated by `npm run data`
public/data/bsb-acts.json
public/data/locations.json
public/data/journeys.geojson
public/data/teachings/index.json
public/data/teachings/*.md

# But DO commit the pre-authored markdown sources (article, sermon, etc.)
!public/data/teachings/sources/
!public/data/teachings/sources/*.md
